This software is a tool to help the users manage their ViewFS partitions 
inside the ViewOS machine. It is not strictly tied to the Virtualsquare
lab (virtualsquare.org) and is an additional external tool. It is not
required to run the base ViewOS machine or ViewFS modules. 

It is a GUI frontend that allows the users the freedom of choosing
which directories to mount (or unmount) through ViewFS (Virtual File System
for ViewOS machines) with several flag of choice. 

This software is released under a GPL license, everyone is free to 
make modifications and branching of this software given they conform to 
the GPL licensing standards (see http://www.gnu.org/licenses/).

Feel free to contact the author of this software at morgawr@gmail.com 
or visit the github repository.

Thanks for using this software.

